c194c9efacd31438","tid":2514306,"uid":30084,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:39:06.000Z","msg":"用下腦喇 橡皮艇過台海<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出煙號都未撚得喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T19:23:16.000Z","msg":"你已經被加入五毛世澤清單"},{"pid":"e16cb7d150347f0408f99e64ac8cb04f0961278c","tid":2514306,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T04:04:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmd8pS3CKEFdRMJCY35x5pJHy5sgxt8kcS4TBgnuQpUm1t?filename=ALn2MKd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FALn2MKd.jpg&h=7c78784f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"894fb746e81f16584d814e64e1c5ebfc000b02c5","tid":2514306,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:15:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210504/EUBRQCDDWFG3BJXVDHHTCLPK4U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210504%2FEUBRQCDDWFG3BJXVDHHTCLPK4U%2F&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOO8Zsbf427MOg7dSrB3lcR0%3D&h=f7c86f08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210504%2FEUBRQCDDWFG3BJXVDHHTCLPK4U%2F&h=8da4bd67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210504/EUBRQCDDWFG3BJXVDHHTCLPK4U/</a><br />\n<br />\n一人之境16小時 閩漢橡皮艇偷渡台中 <br />\n上岸始被截 揭海防漏洞<br />\n<br />\n中國對台灣文攻武嚇日漸升級之際，大陸一名男子聲稱從福建省石獅市出發，駕駛可作軍用的橡皮艇出海，一路如入無人之境，上月30日直抵台灣本島的台中港，投奔自由。目前他正被當地警方調查。過往從大陸偷渡到廈門對出的金門者並非罕見。惟今次偷渡客僅以小艇橫越台灣海峽，出發地與登岸點相距超過185公里，其間未被阻截，暴露台灣海防漏洞。國防部長邱國正承認，偷渡者上岸後才被發現，反映台灣海上偵察及通報機制有缺失，國防部與海巡處需查明原因，彌補缺點。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：偷渡軍用艇 淘寶萬元有售<br />\n<br />\n台灣海峽向來被視為台灣防守的天然屏障，對岸軍隊要跨海登陸並非易事。不過33歲周姓大陸男子，僅憑「淘寶網」上自購價值1.6萬元人民幣（約1.9萬港元）的橡皮艇連引擎，成功登上台中港西碼頭防波堤。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LHGr882_QoSYUBMqgvjsYXogV1s=/510x367/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/G543BIOWMNEM3IOQ7JCYLR5J6M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLHGr882_QoSYUBMqgvjsYXogV1s%3D%2F510x367%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FG543BIOWMNEM3IOQ7JCYLR5J6M.jpg&h=6f0eedcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■周姓男子向警方聲稱偷渡到台灣是為了投奔自由。台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n盼在台自由生活<br />\n<br />\n該名偷渡男子表示，出發當日上午他為橡皮艇注入90公升燃油，沿途風平浪靜，近16小時後於翌日晚登岸。他抵達台中港2小時才被發現。周男表示，事前並無計劃抵台後要幹甚麼，他在台也無親友，只希望在自由的台灣生活。<br />\n<br />\n台中港務警察總隊表示，30日深夜11時50分接報有不明人士逗留，查看後發現大陸男子。警方指，疾控部門已確認其無發燒；現將周男依違反《國家安全法》、《入出國及移民法》移送偵辦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xHG9y6BbTNSyZyzd5tWjNhnzlTk=/510x680/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/V6PKYXE37NF3ZA5KY6A6CHTVEE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxHG9y6BbTNSyZyzd5tWjNhnzlTk%3D%2F510x680%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FV6PKYXE37NF3ZA5KY6A6CHTVEE.jpg&h=bf1f5bba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■大陸男子乘坐圖中橡皮艇花近16小時橫跨台灣海峽偷渡到台中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jn8Z-DDkV6TYb41oXTeJKM7uLuk=/510x382/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HCG5LEPX5NCIPA4WILFEM5KX3I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fjn8Z-DDkV6TYb41oXTeJKM7uLuk%3D%2F510x382%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHCG5LEPX5NCIPA4WILFEM5KX3I.jpg&h=6fc067f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■周男暫時扣押在海巡署隔離。台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民憂暗藏共軍滲透計劃<br />\n<br />\n台海劍拔弩張，小艇卻突破海防抵台，引起台灣朝野擔憂。有立委昨就此質詢當局，國安局副局長胡木源表示，海巡署及台中警方正查證事件。至於橡皮艇是否直接從福建出發，抑或有大船協助，他就稱，各種可能都有。同日邱國正表示，男子上岸後才被發現，代表海上偵察、通報有缺失。被問到事件是否與中共特務測試海防有關，他就指，國防部會「料敵從寬，禦敵從嚴」，從最壞情況思考如何化解。他又否認台軍出現雷達監控疏忽。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。，擔憂橡皮艇渡海來台，暗藏解放軍測試台灣海防或「滲透計劃」。<br />\n<br />\n台灣目前對來自大陸的偷渡客多。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OoU5YfijtLdoNYq3XilzOsX1aH4=/510x457/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N6HX7MHEXFHA7KWDSGA7C4YMFM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOoU5YfijtLdoNYq3XilzOsX1aH4%3D%2F510x457%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN6HX7MHEXFHA7KWDSGA7C4YMFM.gif&h=e26a435a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZD0D2ApUurr3fXo7SDdCYpbNgCw=/312x1782/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WJXSX4W3ZFGRVJNH3XCXRLJALA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZD0D2ApUurr3fXo7SDdCYpbNgCw%3D%2F312x1782%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWJXSX4W3ZFGRVJNH3XCXRLJALA.gif&h=2ece36a1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}